  "texts": [
    "• TPOT Statistics (TPOT recent): Recent time per output token, representing the processing efficiency of the target model.",
    "• Prior Speculation Window Size (γ prev): Speculation window size from the previous iteration, providing temporal context for adaptive adjustment.",
    "The WC-DNN processes this input to produce the optimal prediction for γ.",
    "The compact size of the input feature vector allows the WC-DNN to operate with minimal computational and memory overhead, thereby ensuring fast and efficient adaptation during runtime.",
    "Training the WC-DNN requires labeled data that maps system feature contexts to their optimal window size configurations."
